  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 24a04ab43ec46244e881a610d2970b30, type: 3}
  m_Name: Kael_Quest_3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestInfo
  initialDialog:
  - Greetings, survivor. Look at that dull Iron Sword of yours. Are you planning
    to tickle the monsters out there?
  - To survive in this land, muscle alone won't cut it. You need a sharper weapon.
    Go see the Blacksmith in the central hub; he can help you upgrade your gear.
  - But he will need materials. Let me teach you the secret to finding Gems for forging...
  - Red Gems often drop from ferocious Bears. Green Gems can be found in the cores
    of gooey Slimes. And Blue Gems are hidden within the bandages of Mummies.
  - Do you catch my drift? Gather the materials, visit the Blacksmith, upgrade that
    Iron Sword into a Great Sword Lv1, and bring it back here so I can see it.
  initialDialogClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 282a99ae03df7f645bc3f5eb1817c6bf, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 993a6b072fcf76e4db8f06c0f04f8318, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 85208eea06e59fc49b3266ce18a1f887, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7df418643db3d6f4dacf258336911449, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5bd1b75b75ea8d645a1a5930e6a4ab33, type: 3}
  acceptOption: Got it. I'll go gather the Gems and upgrade my weapon right away!
  acceptAnswer: Excellent! Remember where the monsters roam, and try not to die before
    you bring that Great Sword Lv1 back.
  acceptAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 60845dbb8224e3445a7223ba204e5c94, type: 3}
  declineOption: I'll pass. This Iron Sword is still good enough for me. I'm busy.
  declineAnswer: Suit yourself. Just don't come crying to me when that blade shatters
    in the middle of a monster horde.
  declineAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 187e983c83a2c774a8ff564d489a279f, type: 3}
  comebackAfterDecline: Changed your mind? Ready to learn how to forge a real weapon?
  comebackAfterDeclineClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e2e45889c1bd7514e97a3050128ffeb1, type: 3}
  comebackInProgress: 'You haven''t upgraded your weapon yet? Let me repeat: Red
    Gems from Bears, Green Gems from Slimes, and Blue Gems from Mummies. Go to the
    Blacksmith, craft the Great Sword Lv1, and bring it here.'
  comebackInProgressClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 74fef7ee1e1012349a547125bc6d8910, type: 3}
  comebackCompleted: Well, well! Look at that Great Sword Lv1. The Blacksmith's craftsmanship
    is as good as ever. Now you are truly ready to face real challenges.
  comebackCompletedClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4419cbe1a706f2146a3fdc4f70d83b1f, type: 3}
  finalWords: Don't stop at Lv1. The stronger your weapon, the higher your chances
    of survival. Good luck out there, survivor.
  finalWordsClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2e205857a0e103e41a86329100fa0173, type: 3}
  coinReward: 200
  rewardItem1: Health Potion
  rewardItem2: Great Sword lv1
